For those curious, on PostgreSQL it executes<p><pre><code>    CREATE DATABASE &quot;snapshot&quot; WITH TEMPLATE &quot;source&quot;;
</code></pre>
and on MySQL it loops creates the new database and loops over all the tables running<p><pre><code>    INSERT INTO snapshot.table SELECT * FROM source.table;
</code></pre>
